						<div class="postbody">I talked to John (gamester81) and told him to release or sell his Justice Beaver SNES creation tools when they are done with that project. He said that he would have to talk with the SNES programmer to see if he was interested in doing it. <br /><br />If people are willing to sell their own SNES homebrew tools or do kickstarters to improve or develop SNES tools it would really help the SNES homebrew community and scene.</div>

